-> Two typles of monitoring :
1) Local
2) Centralized (SNMP) simple network monitoring protocol
	- nagios
	- zabex
	- solar events
	- graphana
	- promesthies

-> In AWS
1) Cloud Watch - active monitoring tool - it can alert and take actions as well
2) Cloud Trail - passive monitoring tool - 

>> Unified cloud watch agent (to monitoring OS)

