************* Steps to install unified cloud watch agent (Metrix) ***************

1) sudo yum install amazon-cloudwatch-agent

2) Create IAM roles to use with the CloudWatch agent on Amazon EC2 instancesï»¿.
	- AmazonSSMManagedInstanceCore
	- CloudWatchAgentServerPolicy

3) attach role to ec2

4) Create the CloudWatch agent configuration file with the wizard

5) sudo /opt/aws/amazon-cloudwatch-agent/bin/amazon-cloudwatch-agent-config-wizard

6) Config file : /opt/aws/amazon-cloudwatch-agent/bin/config.json

7) start and run the cloudwatch agent with my config

8) sudo /opt/aws/amazon-cloudwatch-agent/bin/amazon-cloudwatch-agent-ctl -a fetch-config -m ec2 -s -c file:/opt/aws/amazon-cloudwatch-agent/bin/config.json

9) systemctl status amazon-cloudwatch-agent.service

